9】據了解，昨日（4日）確診的第17宗個案、將軍澳醫院的60歲男病人，他的妻子及女兒均對新型冠狀病毒呈陽性反應，屬初步確診個案，兩人將被轉送到瑪嘉烈醫院，令本港確診個案增至20宗。兩母女因出現病徵，昨日在聯合醫院接受隔離治療。據衞生署初步調查，一家三口近日均無外遊紀錄。"},{"pid":"151fae0dbacfafba0449942da480b7056e5109bf","tid":1863343,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735b8ad8dd76fe764af48991e47f5ee9234a149a","tid":1863343,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:02:44.000Z","msg":"20單"},{"pid":"07c7384889ba912cafd89fa7a6028548ede0f49c","tid":1863343,"uid":92908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:03:09.000Z","msg":"幾時到藍屍妻兒"},{"pid":"95ec41953c0baf299ad62cbbc7ddbbc4f38a8ec7","tid":1863343,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:03:13.000Z","msg":"有限度本地人傳人個案 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dee34504db65e54d4f1fd8d37b25011c5978b95","tid":1863343,"uid":281904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac